<br>
The staff i agree should be all/all.<br>
<br>
The red scale hmmm, If i won the red scale as my rogue(he's a gnome) i would trade it to Komm for his BP haha his str suxors! , but on the other hand melee also get chances to roll on other very nice loot(CoF,RBB,and a couple of others). <br>
<br>
 You will always have people who will come to CoG raids in hopes to get the rare loot to sell though. That will never change,but how do you determine &quot;need&quot;. If a rogue wins a RDS and sells it to buy a huge upgrade to his weapon that  he currently has would that be different than a bard/warrior who needs it for his epic ( which is also a huge weapon upgrade).It's all a matter of perspective.Maybe keep names of people who win one so they don't have a chance to get anymore?<br>
<br>
